description: An old-school taco truck with brand new ideas, TacoBar Street is just what you've been looking for! Taking delicious food and throwing it into a tortilla may not be complicated, but when it's right it's right, and TacoBar Street is doing it right! Classic carne asada, delicious potato tacos, bacon and eggs, and so many more are ready and waiting for you, so look for TacoBar Street today!
name: TacoBar Street
